                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980110-58-off316 t17980110-58-cd317"></join>, six pounds weight of tea, value 2l. 2s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17980110-58-victim595" type="victimName">
                  Thomas 
                  Clark
               <interp inst="t17980110-58-victim595" type="surname" value="Clark"></interp>
