                     <interp inst="t17980110-58-person600" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I am a constable: I was sent for to apprehend the prisoner, I took charge of him and the parcel; I had the parcel from Mr. Butterworth.</p>
               <p>Smith. This is the same parcel.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I leave it to the mercy of the Court.</p>
